The '''Uziel system''', also known as the '''Vanqor system''', was a [[Star system/Legends|star system]] located within the [[Sertar sector/Legends|Sertar sector]] of the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]]<ref name="EAOC" /> that contained the [[Planet/Legends|planets]] [[Typha-Dor]], [[Vanqor/Legends|Vanqor]], and [[Zilior]].<ref name="JQ7" /> It was located near the [[Xanlanner system/Legends|Xanlanner system]].<ref name="CSWE">{{CSWECite|III|341|Xanlannes system}}</ref>

